Budget Blue Gold 5 Photo Graduate Announcement

Top 5! Budget Blue Gold 5 Photo Graduate Announcement – Graduation Announcement Cards Popular Budget Blue Gold 5 Photo Graduate Announcement It’s a great choice Budget Blue Gold 5 Photo Graduate Announcement There are many featuresA budget-friendly, modern blue and gold graduation announcement printed on 4.5×5.6" lightweight paper instead of cardstock featuring faux metallic gold calligraphy script typography and graduation cap and personalized with 5 photos (a photo collage of 4 pictures on the front and 1 on the back) against an editable black background color you can change to a school color or favorite color. The class year is editable for other years. The back side features a full-bleed photo and an optional text field for your custom text with details about your graduate. Ideal for conservative budgets and/or hand delivering. Envelopes sold separately on the ordering page. ASSISTANCE: For help with design modification/personalization, color change, transferring the design to another product or if you would like coordinating items, contact the designer BEFORE ORDERING via Zazzle Chat or [email protected].
